import React from 'react'; import './mybite.css'; import Navbar from '../navSection/Navbar'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import Footer from '../footerSection/Footer'; import Masonry, { ResponsiveMasonry } from 'react-responsive-masonry'; import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'; const kitchens = [ { kitchenName: 'WHO GO CHOP RESTAURANTS', timeOpen: 'Open from Mon - Sun 7:00am - 11:00pm', address: '7 olodi street apapa lagos', km: 17, status: 'Available', kitchenImg: '/images/freshfoods.jpg', }, { kitchenName: 'ADOF BUGGERS', timeOpen: 'Open from Mon - Sun 6:00am - 11:00pm', address: '20 kudirat abiola way oregun ikeja lagos', km: 65, status: 'Not available', kitchenImg: '/images/bugerNew.jpg', }, { kitchenName: 'LOAXTIZER FOODs', timeOpen: 'Open from Mon - Sun 11:00am - 12:00pm', address: 'oluwaleyimu street off allen avenue ikeja lagos', km: 5, status: ' available', kitchenImg: '/images/jolofffff.jpg', }, ]; function MyBite() { const {product} = props return (

{kitchens.length} kitchens near you found

{kitchens.map((item, index) => (

{item.kitchenName}

{item?.timeOpen} {item.address} {`${item.km}km away`} {item.status}
))}
); } export default MyBite; // Export the component
